features.name: Better FPS
features.description: Helps improve your FPS in the game, you can remove it if you don't need it or don't like the extra menu.

features.name: Relaxed Dynamic Surroundings
features.description: Checking this will disable a lot of Dynamic Surroundings' features, including some sounds. (You can change this more to your liking in the mod options menu in-game).

features.name: LAN Server Package
features.description: Includes Morpheus for sleep voting and Login Shield

features.name: Borderless Window
features.description: Allows for easier alt-tabbing in borderless windowed mode.

features.name: Sound Filters
features.description: Adds reverb and other sound features to minecraft. This mod is really nice and I would recommend it, but you can disable it if you don't like it.

features.name: Mob Dismemberment
features.description: Have mobs fall into a bunch of body parts (includes blood effects)

features.name: Blur
features.description: Adds a blur effect behind inventories.
